## How to Work

Type `/preset` and describe what you want to do in plain English.

Common tasks:
- "Pull latest changes" — fetches current state from Preset
- "Push my changes" — validates and pushes to Preset
- "Take a screenshot" — captures the dashboard for review
- "Check health" — validates markers and content integrity

## Rules
- Never ask technical questions — auto-resolve using config
- Only ask about business intent, data correctness, and visual specifics
- Check ownership before pushing (warns if editing someone else's section)
- Always validate markers before push (blocks if content regressed)
- Capture screenshots after every push for visual regression tracking

